@wp.kernel
def expr_vmlnlh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.64 / v1 + 0.93)) - 0.55)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.21 * v1 + 0.07)) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.32 - tmp + 0.15)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
